    <pb facs="liv_000965_0001" n="0001"/>
<lb/><!-- G357 (underlined) appearing to the left of 1st 2 address lines, in an unknown hand - how should this be coded? AM --><!-- Added. AW --><opener><add place="inspace" hand="#U" rend="diagonal"><hi rend="underline">G357</hi></add> <dateline rend="right"><placeName>57 Sloane St</placeName>
<lb/><placeName><settlement type="city">London</settlement></placeName> <date when="1857-02-27">27<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi>
<lb/><choice><abbr>Feby</abbr><expan>February</expan></choice> 1857</date></dateline>
<lb/>    
<lb/><salute>My Dear Sir</salute></opener>
<lb rend="center"/><p>I thank you
<lb/>unfeignedly for
<lb/><bibl>your long and
<lb/>interesting letter</bibl> and
<lb/>am sorry I cannot
<lb/>find time to
<lb/>imitate your <w>good-
<lb break="no"/>ness</w> by a suitably
<lb/>long reply</p>

<cb/><ab>
<lb/>I am busy with <bibl>my book</bibl> <bibl>a pamphlet</bibl>
<lb/><choice><sic>publised</sic><corr>published</corr></choice> is not mine
</ab>

    <pb facs="liv_000965_0002" n="0002"/>
<lb/><p>With no one did I
<lb/>anticipate a more
<lb/>interesting meeting
<lb/>than with my late
<lb/>beloved father and
<lb/>with no one would
<lb/>I have enjoyed more
<lb/>the pleasure of <w>con<supplied>-</supplied>
<lb break="no"/>versing</w> on my
<lb/>adventures and
<lb/>labours than unto
<lb/>him but it is not
<lb/>our will but that
<lb/>of the wisest best
<lb/>and kindest that

    <pb facs="liv_000965_0003" n="0003"/>
<lb/>must be done. Good
<lb/>is the will of our
<lb/>most gracious Lord</p>
<lb/><p>My arm about
<lb/>which you kindly
<lb/>enquire is quite
<lb/>well except a joint
<lb/>too many - no 
<lb/>pain or uneasiness
<lb/>but a want of <w>stead-
<lb break="no"/>-iness</w> in <term type="occupation">shooting</term>
<lb/><term type="occupation">welding</term> (i.e. in
<lb/>holding the iron
<lb/>steadily on the anvil
<lb/>and <term type="occupation">carving</term>

    <pb facs="liv_000965_0004" n="0004"/>
<lb/>no operation has
<lb/>been performed &amp;
<lb/>I fear there is no
<lb/>time for any as I
<lb/>must fulfill my
<lb/>engagement with
<lb/>my <orgName>African</orgName> <term type="occupation">attendants</term>
<lb/>One <choice><sic>privelege</sic><corr>privilege</corr></choice> of the
<lb/>making the <persName>Livingstone</persName>
<lb/>name great is the
<lb/>getting more work
<lb/>in scribbling than
<lb/>one mortal man
<lb/>can do.</p> <closer><salute>May God
<lb/>Almighty bless and
<lb/>comfort you</salute><signed><choice><abbr>D.</abbr><expan>David</expan></choice> Livingstone</signed></closer>
            </div>
